## Deployment model
- **Local `azd` only — no GitHub Actions / CI-CD pipelines.**
- The project is deployed from `__PROJECT_NAME__-harness` via `azd up` (`azd provision` for infra,
  `bash scripts/azd-deploy.sh` for services). Container images are built with `az acr build`.
- **Before any deploy, code must be committed, pushed, and version-tagged** in every repo
  (the orchestrator runs `scripts/predeploy-gate.sh`). Do not introduce GitHub Actions workflows,
  self-hosted runners, OIDC deployment secrets, or SHA-named CD here.

